# Case Studies

A collection of real-world creator program, operations, and growth case studies.

Rather than documenting projects chronologically, these case studies focus on decision-making, trade-offs, and scalable program design.

> All examples have been generalized to protect confidential information.

---

## Featured Topics

### 🚀 Creator Programs

- Designing Scalable Incentive Systems
- Building Creator Tier Frameworks
- Creator Lifecycle Management
- Creator Onboarding Strategy

### 📈 Growth

- Increasing Creator Participation
- Campaign Optimization
- Community Activation
- Reward Efficiency

### ⚙️ Operations

- Scaling Operations
- Cross-functional Collaboration
- Workflow Optimization
- Automation

### 📊 Strategy

- Resource Allocation
- Prioritization
- Metrics & Measurement
- Program Iteration

---

Each article follows the same structure:

- Background
- Problem
- Constraints
- Decision
- Execution
- Outcome
- Lessons Learned
- AI Reflection
